As we remember, Kim Jong-il’s plane was impressed and waved the hand mostly towards Russia’s side. That doesn’t change the fact that Friendship supposedly lasts forever. If not for that friendship, then only North Korea would be a nuclear state.

Because of Mr Putin, the political routes from the Russian Federation to North Korea have become larger in size than what they are for China. It’s tradition for Russo-North Korean ties to be prejudicial as those between nations. They have never defined themselves only as economic ties. Mr Putin lifted delegations from the two states very high. Mr Putin’s trips often include short stays for recreational purposes. And indeed, Mr Belavia aeroplane used to land in Vladivostok and not in Moscow, so as to avoid the dozens letters they used to receive from North Koreans desiring to see Kim Jong-il.

From Different Centries, for a Better Life

Yu Sin Dong becomes his father. The land looks vast faraway from the Blue City, so the man breathes some fresh air there. The Russian border is like a barbed wire now. Belgian and American tanks are on the other side. Now neither steel wire nor train is constructed on the Russian side of the border, while on the Chinese side the train rides to Seoul and Dandong.
